{"tid":884884,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇手足打算今年寄聖誕卡去中原比施老闆？","createTime":"2018-11-01T02:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T00:09:37.000Z","uid":54870,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f86a276b72123094f71d31942e84e535b06f8f57","tid":884884,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:57:46.000Z","msg":"下款記得要用塗改液改番自己個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n施永青提「聖誕」：X你老母<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聖誕前各公司互送聖誕卡、果籃，聊表心意，不過中原地產創辦人施永青對「聖誕」就有HardFeeling，《壹週刊》報道，施永青一聽到「聖誕」無名火起：「我最憎就是聖誕！」，細個因為屋企窮，無錢買聖誕卡買，所以他將人哋送畀佢張聖誕卡，改咗自己個名送畀人，點知同學將件事唱通街，超慘！仲話，「我已經同佢反左面架喇！」<br />\n<br />\n依家施永青財力雄厚，想送幾多果籃塞住人哋把口都得啦！佢話雖然收大把果籃，但一個都唔會送出去，仲好激動咁話，「你咪唔好同我做生意囉，笨！我X你老母」嚇到個記者打咗個突，童年的影響之大，真係唔講得笑！"},{"pid":"0a33a9fda519e74793b440ae042acfe511e6f363","tid":884884,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T03:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72cccbd8fdcc5d90b39be3fedd2fc17a3b46dd24","tid":884884,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:28:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e316e9d487db1f10183835347fa9d2b246008e","tid":884884,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T00:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}